'''哈罗北京國際學校'''（{{lang-en|Harrow International School Beijing}}）是一所位于[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[北京市|北京市]][[朝阳区_(北京)|朝阳区]][[崔各庄地区|崔各庄地区]]何各庄村的国际学校<ref>"[http://www.harrowbeijing.cn/contact-us.aspx Contact Us] {{Wayback|url=http://www.harrowbeijing.cn/contact-us.aspx |date=20150312035709 }}." 哈罗北京國際學校. "HARROW International School Beijing No.287 Hegezhuang Village, Cuigezhuang County, Chaoyang District, Beijing, China 100102 北京市朝阳区崔各庄乡何各庄村287号, 邮编: 100102" - [http://www.harrowbeijing.cn/upload/AboutUs/Hegezhuang/HarrowMapDirections2013email.jpg Map] {{Wayback|url=http://www.harrowbeijing.cn/upload/AboutUs/Hegezhuang/HarrowMapDirections2013email.jpg |date=20160303214336 }}</ref>，2005年建立，是[[哈罗公学|哈罗公学]]所属学校，使用[[英文|英文]]教学。<ref>{{cite news|author=Pocha, Jehangir S.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/15/world/asia/15iht-schools.3547208.html?_r=0|title=In China, a Western-style education has appeal - Asia - Pacific - International Herald Tribune|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005020148/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/15/world/asia/15iht-schools.3547208.html?_r=0|archive-date=2013-10-05|newspaper=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|date=2006-08-15}}</ref>

2022年因为中国法哈罗北京更名到《北京市朝阳区礼德学校》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/539534301_691021|title=哈罗北京“重启”礼德品牌，4月底前北京民办学校陆续更名|work=[[搜狐|搜狐]]|date=2022-04-20|accessdate=2022-05-16|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516150737/https://www.sohu.com/a/539534301_691021}}</ref>

